timeless the soundtrack of this movie was undoubtedly instrumental in making empire of the sun the amazingly beautiful movie that it is . with the first track alone , suo gan , which is actually a welsh lullaby and not a japanese song , you 'll find yourself riveted and drawn to the time and place and story of jim . the beauty of listening to this soundtrack is sitting back , and reliving the scenes from the movie in your head . it is timeless , bittersweet and triumphant all in one